{"tid":647070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何 家 四 姨 太 對 腳 幼 過 手 臂 痴 撚 線 㗎😱😱😱","createTime":"2018-04-29T14:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T03:41:22.000Z","uid":24160,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1be83051a13595c94d3addf308c34fa620ceb217","tid":647070,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/221910_c0ee7f1f902d4a96bb208f76699f128d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F221910_c0ee7f1f902d4a96bb208f76699f128d.png&h=735fc551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/222121_9be8ead90f060b649a68e75aaa8a18fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F222121_9be8ead90f060b649a68e75aaa8a18fc.png&h=4d27b826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72b214f7a0fa8e6c62722c1011cd702de736ee4","tid":647070,"uid":24160,"like":36,"dislike":4,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/222512_c07eba0aa2c9b1fbd2321beb7e20c524.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F222512_c07eba0aa2c9b1fbd2321beb7e20c524.png&h=f276e2f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同場重有熟霉姐出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7m3mv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7m3mv.jpg&h=33132a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n考試面試見客演講決策<br />\n你同我每日都會面對<br />\n咁係呢啲咁重要既時刻<br />\n究竟我地點樣可以保持冷靜<br />\n迎接每一個難關呢<br />\n淑梅姐 你有啲咩對策可以應付啊<br />\n其實呢好多時係開 mic 啊做 show 之前我都會好緊張㗎<br />\n直至到我用左英國巴哈急救寧<br />\n佢係種天然既鎮靜劑嚟㗎<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/CMrrzki.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FCMrrzki.gif&h=a36df928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食一粒之後呢<br />\n好快情緒就會冷靜落嚟<br />\n精神自然更加集中啦<br />\n特別果啲考試啊面試啊見客之前呢<br />\n食一粒幫助佢地舒緩情緒<br />\n面對挑戰<br />\n呢個產品啊係英國已經有成七十幾年歷史㗎喇<br />\n成分天然安全可靠<br />\n大人小朋友都啱用㗎喎<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Wb40tOP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FWb40tOP.gif&h=4251cdeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就連英國皇室都用緊添㗎<br />\n另外呢我想問下楊校長<br />\n壓力呢又會影響睡眠喎<br />\n其實可以點樣處理啊<br />\n其實工作真係好繁忙㗎<br />\n返到屋企仲 住學校既工作<br />\n就搞到夜晚訓唔著<br />\n自從用左英國巴哈甜睡寧<br />\n只要臨瞓之前係脷底噴兩下<br />\n好快就訓著<br />\n夜晚仲唔會紮醒添<br />\n佢成分天然<br />\n加上百栗花既精華<br />\n好快就令我地鬆弛神經<br />\n促進我地既深層睡眠<br />\n佢無副作用<br />\n亦都唔會造成依賴<br />\n咁我哋瞓醒覺<br />\n第二日就能夠精神奕奕咁繼續工作㗎喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zujAP31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzujAP31.jpg&h=37e8223b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e3219105dda96cb936aa1c81c820a7aa8f70cef","tid":647070,"uid":145690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"熟梅姐 有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d779465f6aa4b997d8896ff8a948066e6339ad","tid":647070,"uid":24160,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3e3219105dda96cb936aa1c81c820a7aa8f70cef","tid":647070,"uid":145690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"熟梅姐 有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:29:59.000Z","msg":"靚女到呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3xDsGOS6-DY/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F3xDsGOS6-DY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=6f7525f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f08bd5ea14942a29b167f1f4c4c8c492ece9cdd","tid":647070,"uid":24160,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"邊個大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熟霉姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿蛆<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0MFMoeC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0MFMoeC.gif&h=f8096ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PxX9YhF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPxX9YhF.gif&h=1912b929&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48e1cfc810acdf2d17a3396e973069c5a85332c8","tid":647070,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e59b0863165be3ebbc6db503b8bfa89afa82766","tid":647070,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:38:32.000Z","msg":"四太係咪比人p左圖 好瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ade432449664bcbe8fd7015006b900d862b3af","tid":647070,"uid":114692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e3a5b86ab007dbe3c8534e86e18b8acaf2